race.comment: SAINT TAY (6) ran a good time (25.77) when placing three back at Ballarat but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing sixth (22.50) at this track. Key player on best and worth another chance. MORAINE SADIE (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (24.00) in a Grade 5 at Horsham. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Warrants plenty of respect. AMINAH (7) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (30.53) last time in a T3 Grade 5 H at Sandown. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Shapes as one to consider. Something for the Multiples: ASTON MONSOON (3)
